title: Uluru resort deal sparks call for reforms after millions lost in Indigenous Land Corporation acquisition
text: Millions of taxpayer dollars lost when the Indigenous Land Corporation purchased Ayers Rock Resort near Uluru in 2010 demonstrates "urgent need" for reforms to the way federal statutory authorities are regulated, the corporation's outgoing chair says. ...
